\r\n- High-speed access of users to information resources of global networks through the central Internet node of the university;\r\n- Access of \"external\" users to the centralized information resources of the university;\r\n- Distance learning system, etc.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1032\" src=\"https://wp.scs.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/images_1112-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" />\r\n<h4><strong> Project Development Plan: </strong></h4>\r\nFor the development of the material base (renovation, modernization and repair) of the department SPiSKS FPM in the current year planned to spend about 140 000 UAH. UAH 127,393 was actually spent, and UAH 85,133. of which was spent on renovations.\r\n\r\n<strong> Planned: </strong>\r\n- Replacement of computer class monitors №117 / 1 with 20 ”TFT monitors - 12 pcs.\r\n- Replacement of 10 obsolete (2000-2002 year of release) PC) and their transfer to other divisions of NTTU KPI.\r\n- Acquisition and installation of a case for servers - 1 piece\r\n- Equipment of a grounding contour and connection of computer classes to a contour.\r\n- Acquisition of Notebook (ACER Aspire 5920G-934G25Bn) - 5 pcs\r\n- Purchase of USB Flash memory modules (2-4 gb) - 5 pcs\r\n- Purchase of printers - 5 pcs\r\n- Contract renewal MSDN AA.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Material base of the unit', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'material-base-of-the-unit', '', '', '2021-06-05 07:23:34', '2021-06-05 07:23:34', '', 0, 'https://scs.wp.its-my.site/?page_id=29', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(30, 1, '2021-02-09 16:27:42', '2021-02-09 16:27:42', '<div id=\"node-311\" class=\"node node-page\">\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\n<div class=\"field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden\">\n<div class=\"field-items\">\n<div class=\"field-item even\">\n<p style=\"color: # 494949;  \"><span style=\"\"> Content of activities of specialists in the educational program 123 - COMPUTER ENGINEERING is to create <em> hardware and software </em> of modern and advanced information technologies, development and application of <em> computer systems and components of general and special purpose </em>, their system software, <em> specialized computer systems and networks </em> with optimized parameters, <em> embedded computer systems </em>, technical <em> means of information protection </em> in computer systems, local and distributed computer systems. </span></p>\n\n<div style=\"color: # 494949;  \">\n<p style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0px;   color: # b01717;\" align=\"center\">External EIT Certificates <strong> for Foreign Language </strong> for 2018, 2019 and 2020 are credited.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0px;   color: # b01717;\" align=\"center\">External EIT certificates are credited for 2017, 2018, 2019 and 2020.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0px;   color: # b01717;\" align=\"center\"><strong> List of External Evaluation for Educational Program 123 \"Computer Engineering\": </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"color: # 494949;  \">\n<p style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0px;   color: # b01717;\" align=\"center\"><strong> (<a href=\"https://pk.kpi.ua/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/bl_2020-030220.pdf\"> source </a>) </strong></p>\n\n<table class=\"rtab\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1em 0px; width: 543px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; table-layout: fixed;  \" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody style=\"border-top: 1px solid #cccccc;\">\n<tr align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"# D5D5D5\">\n<td class=\"tdo2\" style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; width: 122px; background: # d8e5fc; font-weight: 600;  \">List of competitive subjects (entrance examinations, creative competitions)</td>\n<td class=\"tdo2\" style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; width: 122px; background: # d8e5fc; font-weight: 600;  \">Weight of EIT certificate items (К1, К2, К3)</td>\n<td class=\"tdo2\" style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; width: 122px; background: # d8e5fc; font-weight: 600;  \">Weight of the certificate of complete general secondary education (К4)</td>\n<td class=\"tdo2\" style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; width: 122px; background: # d8e5fc; font-weight: 600;  \">The weight of the score for the successful completion of the preparatory courses ZVO (K5)</td>\n<td class=\"tdo2\" style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; width: 121px; background: # d8e5fc; font-weight: 600;  \">Minimum number of points for admission to the competition or for enrollment in the quota</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border: 1px solid windowtext; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\">1. Ukrainian language and literature</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\">0.25</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\" rowspan=\"3\">0</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\" rowspan=\"3\">0</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 121px;\">125</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border: 1px solid windowtext; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" align=\" center \">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\">2. Mathematics</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\">0.5</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 121px;\">125</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"border: 1px solid windowtext; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\">3. Physics or foreign language *</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 122px;\">0.25</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-style: solid; border-color: initial; background: # d8e5fc;   width: 121px;\">125</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<table style=\"\" border=\"0\" width=\"693\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<thead>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<th style=\"width: 689px;\" colspan=\"3\">Stages of the introductory campaign\n\n(entrants based on complete general secondary education)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Start of registration of electronic offices of entrants, download of appendices to documents on full general secondary education</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 1, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Start accepting applications and documents</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 13, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Completion of applications and documents from entrance examiners</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 22, 2020, 18-00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Completion of applications and documents based on EIT</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 22, 2020, 18-00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Terms of entrance examinations (interviews)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 17 - July 19, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Terms of publication of the rating list of entrants with the indication of recommended for enrollment in the places of the state order</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than July 27, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Expiry of the deadline for entrants to enroll in public procurement places</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than 18.00 on July 31, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Expiration of the deadline for entrants who have received a recommendation to enroll in places financed by individuals and legal entities</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than 17.00 on August 06, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 187px;\" rowspan=\"2\">Deadlines for enrollment</td>\n<td style=\"width: 341px;\">by government order</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than 12.00 on August 1, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 341px;\">at the expense of individuals and legal entities</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later\n\nAugust 7, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n* at 18-00 July 16 - for persons who enter on the basis of an interview, entrance exams, creative competitions; at 18-00 July 22 - for persons entering by the results of external independent evaluation, exams, creative competitions, held from 01 to 12 July; entrance exams, creative competitions are held in several streams from 01 to 12 July inclusive (for entrants to state and regional orders on a schedule to be sent by March 15 for monitoring review to the Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine). In the period from 17 to 22 July, additional sessions of exams, creative competitions may be held for entrants who take their places at the expense of individuals and / or legal entities. Mechanisms for registration of participants in creative competitions, entrance exams, their organization and conduct are determined in accordance with the law; interviews are held on July 17;\n\n** The publication of the lists of persons recommended for enrollment based on the results of the interview, with notification of their receipt or non-receipt of the right to obtain higher education by state order, is carried out no later than 12:00 on July 20. Applicants who have received recommendations must comply with the requirements for enrollment in public procurement places by 10:00 am on July 22, as well as submit a written application for exclusion of applications for other public procurement sites. Enrollment of this category of entrants by state order takes place no later than 15-00 o\'clock on July 22. Applications of enrolled persons to other places of the state order are excluded during July 22;\n\n*** if available invacancies, by decision of the Admissions Committee, the terms may be extended.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n</div>', 'Admission to the 1st year', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'admission-to-the-1st-year', '', '', '2021-05-23 23:23:27', '2021-05-23 23:23:27', '', 0, 'https://scs.wp.its-my.site/?page_id=30', 3, 'page', '', 0),
(31, 1, '2021-02-09 16:34:52', '2021-02-09 16:34:52', '<div id=\"node-234\" class=\"node node-page\">\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\n<div class=\"field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden\">\n<div class=\"field-items\">\n<div class=\"field-item even\">\n<div style=\"color: # 041347;   padding: 5px; margin: 5px; text-align: center;\">\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong> <span style=\" color: # b01717;\"> RECEPTION AT FPM FOR THE PROGRAM\nPREPARATION OF THE MASTER FOR THE EDUCATIONAL PROGRAM </span> </strong>\n\n<strong style=\"\"> <span style=\" color: # b01717;\"> 123 - \"COMPUTER ENGINEERING\" </span> </strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n<table style=\"width: 90.0829%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> Admission for training programs &lt; strong&gt; master\'s full-time study is carried out in the educational program <strong> COMPUTER ENGINEERING </strong> in the following specializations: </span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong style=\"\">\" Computer Systems and Components \", </strong> </span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong style=\"\">\" System Programming \", </strong> </span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong style=\"\">\" Specialized Computer Systems \". </strong> </span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> Admission plan <em> by state order </em> (full-time form of study) is determined by the Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine. </span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"color: # ff0000;\"> <span style=\"\"> There is no set for OQR \"Specialist\"! </span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong style=\"color: # b01717; \"> <span style=\"\"> <span style=\"color: # 800000;\"> <a style=\"color: # b01717;\" href=\"http://pk.kpi.ua/\"> Official documents of the selection committee </a>: </span> </span> </strong> </span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"\" align=\"left\"><strong style=\" \"> <span style=\"color: # 800000;\"> PROGRAM of complex professional test for admission to the educational-professional training program of the master of specialty 123 - Comp computer engineering in the specializations \"Computer Systems and Components\", \"System Programming\", \"Specialized Computer Systems\" is </span> <u> <a href=\"sites / default / files / files / 2020 /% D0% 92% D1% 81% D1% 82% D1% 83% D0% BF / Prog_KI_2020.doc\"> <span style=\"color: # 800000;\"> at this link </span> </a> <a href=\"sites/default/files/files/Prog_IPZ-2019-1.pdf\"> <u> <span style=\"color: # 800000;\">. </span> </u> </a></u></strong></p>\n\n<div style=\"\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <span style=\"color: # 800000;\"> <b> PROGRAM of additional test for admission to the educational-professional training program of the master\'s specialty 123 - Computer Engineering in the specializations\" Computer Systems and Components \",\" System Programming \",\" Specialized Computer Systems \"is </b> </span> <a href=\"sites/default/files/files/2020/%D0%92%D1%81%D1%82%D1%83%D0%BF/Prog_KI_dod_2020-1.docx\"> <u> <span style=\"color: # 800000;\"> by this link </span></u></a></span> <a href=\"http://scs.kpi.ua/sites/default/files/files/2020/%D0%92%D1%81%D1%82%D1%83%D0%BF/Prog_KI_dod_2020-1.docx\"> <u> <span style=\"font-weight: bold; color: # 800000;\">. </span> </u> </a></span></p>\n\n</div>\n<strong> <span style=\"color: # 000000; \"> <span style=\"\"> Documents for admission to the master\'s degree in 2020 year: </span> </span> </strong>\n\n<a href=\"https://pk.kpi.ua/entry-5-course/\"> <span style=\"color: # ff0000;\"> <span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> General questions of admission to the master\'s program </span> </span> </span> </a>\n\n<a style=\"\" href=\"sites / default / files / files / popis наук-праць.pdf\"> <span style=\"color: # ff0000; \"> <span style=\"font- size: 16px;\"> Example of registration of the list of scientific works of the entrant </span> </span> </a>\n<div style=\"\"></div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" width: 100%;\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n</div>', 'Admission to the master\'s degree', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'admission-to-the-master-s-degree', '', '', '2021-05-23 23:23:45', '2021-05-23 23:23:45', '', 0, 'https://scs.wp.its-my.site/?page_id=31', 2, 'page', '', 0);
