(490, 1, '2021-03-24 15:10:23', '2021-03-24 15:10:23', '<div class=\"field-item even\">\n\n<strong> <span style=\" \"> Samples of required documents: </span> </strong>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_DocsZahMagONP_Zayava_na_robotu.docx\"> <span style=\"font- family: times new roman, times, serif;\"> <strong> <span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> Statement on the topic of master\'s dissertation </span> </span></strong> </span> </a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_DocsZahMagONP_Tytul_mag_dis.doc\"> <span style=\"font- size: 14px;\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong> Master\'s thesis title page </strong> </span> </span> </a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_DocsZahMagONP_zavdanya_na_MD_20.doc\"> <span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong> Master\'s dissertation (MD) </strong> </span> </span></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_DocsZahMagONP_Rezulytatu_ocinyuvannya_mag_dis.docx\"> <span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong> Leader Scoreboard Template </strong> </span> </span> </a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_DocsZahMagONP_Vidguk_kerivnuk.doc\"> <span style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> <strong> MD Head\'s Response </strong> </span> </span> </a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_DocsZahMagONP_Recensiya_MD.doc\">Review of MD</a>\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><span style=\"\"> <b> 7 days (weeks) before protection </b> </span></p>\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><span style=\"\"> <strong> need to submit documents to the EC Secretary </strong> </span></p>\n<p class=\"rtecenter\"><span style=\"\"> <strong> (room 112-15 to Boyarinova Yuliya Yevgenivna) </strong> </span></p>\n1. <strong> Paperback and signed master\'s thesis </strong>\n\nThe structure of the master\'s thesis:\n\n· <strong> <u> Title page </u> </strong> with specialty <strong> <u> 123 Computer Engineering </u> </strong>\n\n<strong> <u> Computer Systems and Components </u> </strong>\n\nor <strong> <u> System Programming </u> </strong>\n\nor <strong> <u> Specialized Computer Systems </u> </strong>),\n\ntopics, name of student, supervisor, consultants, reviewer, etc., where <strong> all signatures must be </strong>;\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· <strong> <u> TASKS on MD </u> </strong> with mandatory number and date order</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"background-color: #afeeee;\"> (</span> <strong> <u> <span style=\"background-color: #afeeee;\"> №3298-C from 12 .11 . 2020 y.</span></u></strong><span style=\"background-color: #afeeee;\">) </span> </span> and calendar plan;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· <strong><u> ABSTRACT</u> </strong> (Ukrainian, English languages ​​on separate sheets)</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· <strong> <u> EXPLANATORY NOTE </u> </strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· <strong> <u> APPENDICES </u> </strong> (presentation, listing of program (s), copies of publications, implementation certificate, if any)</p>\n2. <strong> MD CD </strong>\n\nThe information recorded on the disk should be structured as follows:\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· TEXT folder;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· PROGRAM folder;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· PREZENTATION folder</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 33.5pt;\">· WEBSITE folder (contains a file with an abstract in two languages ​​and a file with TEXT information about DEVELOPMENT, which will be placed on the website of the department).</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 35.45pt;\"><span style=\" \"> The disk must be signed by the manager. This disc must be enclosed in an envelope attached to the cover of the MD. </span></p>\n3. <strong> Bookbinding copies of presentation slides </strong>\n\n5. <strong> Review </strong>\n\n6. <strong> Supervisor Response </strong>\n\n7. <strong> Scorebook </strong>\n\n8. <strong> Certificate of implementation (if any) </strong>\n\n<strong>9.  Master\'s Thesis Evaluation Results </strong>\n\n<strong> <span style=\" \"> Persons whose MD is not signed by the head of the department are NOT ALLOWED to defend! </span> </strong>\n\n<strong> <span style=\" \"> Penalty points will be imposed for late submission of the above documents, as well as for their improper execution (see table) </span></strong>\n\n<strong><strong> <u> Procedure for preparing MD for protection </u> &lt; / strong&gt;</strong></strong>\n<ol>\n 	<li>The bound MD is signed by the author, supervisor, reviewer.</li>\n 	<li>The CD with the MD materials is signed by the supervisor and glued in an envelope on the MD cover.</li>\n 	<li>MD together with the review, response and table of evaluation results from the head (link to the sample in electronic form see above) and graphic materials (presentation), a certificate of borrowing is provided to the secretary of the examination commission to place MD materials on the department\'s website. &gt;</li>\n 	<li>After the materials of MD will be posted on the website of the department - the secretary certifies it with his signature in the table of evaluation results.</li>\n 	<li>MD together with all the necessary documentation remains with the Secretary of the examination commission for submission to the EC ..</li>\n 	<li>MD protection is on schedule.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>', 'Master ESP Docs', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'master-esp-docs__trashed', '', '', '2021-06-04 21:41:24', '2021-06-04 21:41:24', '', 0, 'https://scs.wp.its-my.site/?page_id=490', 11, 'page', '', 0);
