topology, structure and organization of computer systems, perform adaptation for specialized applications, develop computer system interfaces, etc.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Graduates can work system administrators and programmers, network administrators, specialists in the development, maintenance or operation of hardware and software of computer systems and networks for various purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Graduates work in many organizations, including Ukrtelecom, Softline, Softronic, UMC, UTEL, KyivStar GSM, Kvazar-Micro; Ukrainian Anti-Virus Center, Research Institutes of the National Academy of Sciences of Ukraine; Ukrainian banks - \"National Bank of Ukraine\", \"Nadra\", \"Ukrsotsbank\", \"Pravexbank\", \"Expobank\", \"Oschadbank\"; scientific and analytical subdivisions of the Security Service of Ukraine, the Ministry of Internal Affairs, customs and tax services of Ukraine; Ministry of Finance, Supreme Court, other state and non-state enterprises, IT companies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Department of System Programming and Specialized Computer Systems, Faculty of Applied Mathematics, NTUU \"Igor Sikorsky KPI\"', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '663-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-23 22:53:32', '2021-05-23 22:53:32', '', 663, 'https://wp.scs.its-my.site/?p=680', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
