(739, 1, '2021-05-23 23:18:45', '2021-05-23 23:18:45', '<div class=\"field-item even\">\n<p class=\"rteleft\">To support the teaching of professional disciplines, teachers of the department have developed and used distance learning courses, including the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n 	<li class=\"rteleft\">Local Area Networks</li>\n 	<li class=\"rteleft\">System Programming</li>\n 	<li class=\"rteleft\">Internet Protocols</li>\n 	<li class=\"rteleft\">and others</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"rtejustify\">Distance disciplines are listed on the website of the Ukrainian Institute of Information Technology in Education. National Technical University of Ukraine \"KPI\" <u> <a href=\"http://uiite.kpi.ua\"> http://uiite.kpi.ua </a> </u> in the section <u> Distance courses - &amp; gt; Technical disciplines </u>.</p>\n<p class=\"rtejustify\">In addition, teachers of the department have prepared electronic teaching materials for various disciplines. They are posted on the websites of teachers, in the archives of the sites of the department and faculty and are available to students.</p>\n\n</div>', 'Distance learning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '144-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-23 23:18:45', '2021-05-23 23:18:45', '', 144, 'https://wp.scs.its-my.site/?p=739', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(740, 1, '2021-05-23 23:18:49', '2021-05-23 23:18:49', '<div id=\"node-32\" class=\"node node-page\">\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\n<div class=\"field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden\">\n<div class=\"field-items\">\n<div class=\"field-item even\">\n\n<span style=\"\"> Postgraduate students of the department </span>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em; padding: 0px 35px;  line-height: 1.2em; text-indent: 4px; color: # 000000;  text-align: justify;\">12 teachers of the department have the right to supervise the scientific work of graduate students.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em; padding: 0px 35px;  line-height: 1.2em; text-indent: 4px; color: # 000000;  text-align: justify;\">During the existence of the department its staff and graduates have defended 3 doctoral and 17 candidate dissertations.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2em; padding: 0px 35px;  line-height: 1.2em; text-indent: 4px; color: # 000000;  text-align: justify;\">Currently, the following postgraduate students study at the Department of Postgraduate Studies in PhD:</p>\n&nbsp;\n<table class=\"tableWide\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;  text-align: left; border-collapse: collapse; width: 759px;\">\n<tbody style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n<tr class=\"tableCaption\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: #dddddd;\">\n<td style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 2px ridge; width: 74px;\">Year of entry</td>\n<td style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 2px ridge; width: 189px;\">Surname, patronymic</td>\n<td style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 2px ridge; width: 271px;\">Topics of dissertations (PhD) of graduate students of the department</td>\n<td style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 2px ridge; width: 70px;\">Graduation</td>\n<td style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 2px ridge; width: 90px;\">Supervisor</td>\n<td style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0