ral secondary education</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 1, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Start accepting applications and documents</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 13, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Completion of applications and documents from entrance examiners</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 22, 2020, 18-00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Completion of applications and documents based on EIT</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 22, 2020, 18-00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Terms of entrance examinations (interviews)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">July 17 - July 19, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Terms of publication of the rating list of entrants with the indication of recommended for enrollment in the places of the state order</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than July 27, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Expiry of the deadline for entrants to enroll in public procurement places</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than 18.00 on July 31, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 530px;\" colspan=\"2\">Expiration of the deadline for entrants who have received a recommendation to enroll in places financed by individuals and legal entities</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than 17.00 on August 06, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 187px;\" rowspan=\"2\">Deadlines for enrollment</td>\n<td style=\"width: 341px;\">by government order</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later than 12.00 on August 1, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n<tr align=\"center\">\n<td style=\"width: 341px;\">at the expense of individuals and legal entities</td>\n<td style=\"width: 157px;\">no later\n\nAugust 7, 2020</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n* at 18-00 July 16 - for persons who enter on the basis of an interview, entrance exams, creative competitions; at 18-00 July 22 - for persons entering by the results of external independent evaluation, exams, creative competitions, held from 01 to 12 July; entrance exams, creative competitions are held in several streams from 01 to 12 July inclusive (for entrants to state and regional orders on a schedule to be sent by March 15 for monitoring review to the Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine). In the period from 17 to 22 July, additional sessions of exams, creative competitions may be held for entrants who take their places at the expense of individuals and / or legal entities. Mechanisms for registration of participants in creative competitions, entrance exams, their organization and conduct are determined in accordance with the law; interviews are held on July 17;\n\n** The publication of the lists of persons recommended for enrollment based on the results of the interview, with notification of their receipt or non-receipt of the right to obtain higher education by state order, is carried out no later than 12:00 on July 20. Applicants who have received recommendations must comply with the requirements for enrollment in public procurement places by 10:00 am on July 22, as well as submit a written application for exclusion of applications for other public procurement sites. Enrollment of this category of entrants by state order takes place no later than 15-00 o\'clock on July 22. Applications of enrolled persons to other places of the state order are excluded during July 22;\n\n*** if available invacancies, by decision of the Admissions Committee, the terms may be extended.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n</div>', 'Admission to the 1st year', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '30-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-23 23:23:08', '2021-05-23 23:23:08', '', 30, 'https://wp.scs.its-my.site/?p=753