>)</span></span></p>\nBachelor\'s degree in computer engineering 2015 2015р.\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href=\"sites/default/files/materials/osvitnistandarti/nakaz_lists.rar\">Order, letters of approval</a></li>\n 	<li><a href=\"sites/default/files/materials/osvitnistandarti/OKX_BAK_2011.pdf\">Educational and qualification characteristics of CI 2011</a></li>\n 	<li><a href=\"sites/default/files/materials/osvitnistandarti/OPP_BAK_2011.pdf\">Educational and professional characteristics of CI 2011</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-item form-type-item\"><label>language </label> Undefined</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Bachelors', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-04 20:27:52', '2021-06-04 20:27:52', '', 154, 'https://wp.scs.its-my.site/?p=898', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
