03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Savchuk.doc\">Савчук А.О. Web-ресурс Інтернет-магазину SANSERV</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Strashnuh.docx\">Страшних Д.В. Сross-платформна  система мобільного додатку арт-галереї</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Zhelizko.doc\">Желізко А.А. Система обліку споживання енергоносіїв та води у комунальному господарстві</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Karpovich.docx\">Карповіч О.М. Розподілена система пошуку оптимальних маршрутів в галузі логістики. Android-додаток</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Mosiy.docx\">Мосійчук І.В.  Алгоритм та програма визначення кількості попарних реберних циклів</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Nikitash.docx\">Нікіташ В.В. Розподілена система пошуку оптимальних маршрутів в галузі логістики. Серверна підсистема</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Tymofienko.docx\">Тимофієнко К.Ю. Алгоритм виявлення невизначеностей при тестуванні багатопроцесорних систем</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Oliynuk.docx\">Олійник М.Є. Алгоритм та програма генерування рівновагових двійкових векторів</a>\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Burnas.docx\">Бурнас Руслан Геннадійович. Web-орієнтована система підтримки форумів</a></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Kovtun.docx\">Ковтун Олександр Олександрович. Керований генератор рівно-вагових псевдовипадкових двійкових наборів</a></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Paliy.doc\">Палій Ілля Олегович. Модифікація моделі поведінки багатопроцесорної системи у потоку відмов</a></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Banit.doc\">Баніт Віталій Віталійович.  Web-додаток «Соціальна мережа університету»</a></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Leus.doc\">Леус Артем Васильович.  Програма  паралельної обробки інтенсивних потоків даних</a></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Rodin.docx\">Родін Артем Михайлович. Програмний додаток редагування та обробки музичних записів</a></p>\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/images_BacArticleDocs2015_Hyschenko.doc\">Хищенко Євгеній Дмитрович. Система аналізу часу роботи програм</a>\n\n</div>', 'Анотації захищених бакалаврських робіт - 2015', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '244-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-04 21:45:36', '2021-06-04 21:45:36', '', 244, 'https://wp.scs.its-my.site/?p=974', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(975, 1, '2021-06-04 21:45:49', '2021-06-04 21:45:49', '<div class=\"field-item even\">\n<p class=\"xfmc1\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"UK\" style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"><span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"uk\" data-phrase-index=\"0\">Normocontrol</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"xfmc1\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"UK\" style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> (DP signature) </span> </span></p>\n<p class=\"xfmc1\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"UK\" style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> 4th year </span> </span></p>\n<p class=\"xfmc1\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"UK\" style=\"\"> <span style=\"\"> Klyatchenko Ya.M. 104 / 1-15 </span> </span></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong> <span style=\"\"> Samples of required documents: </span> </strong>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_BakalavrDP2020_05_2020.docx\">Bachelor\'s DP degree</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_BakalavrDR2020_05-2020.docx\">Bachelor\'s DM degree</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_ZavdanyaDP2020_05-2020.docx\"> Tasks for DP </a>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"> <a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_Tytul_DP_Bakalavr2020.docx\"> <span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"uk\" data-phrase-index=\"0\">Bachelor\'s degree title for students of NMK \"IPO\"</span></span><span style=\"color: # ff8c00;\">\n</span> </a> </span>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_Zavdanya_DP_Bakalavr-2020.docx\"><span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\" style=\"color: #ff6600;\"> <span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"uk\" data-phrase-index=\"0\">Tasks at the State Enterprise for students of NMK \"IPO\"</span></span><span style=\"color: # ff8c00;\">\n</span></a>\n\n<a title=\"Table template with points from supervisor for bachelor\" href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_Tabl_Bakalavr_2020.docx\"> <span style=\"color: # 0000ff;\"><span class=\"VIiyi\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"JLqJ4b ChMk0b\" data-language-for-alternatives=\"en\" data-language-to-translate-into=\"uk\" data-phrase-index=\"0\">Table template with points from supervisor for bachelor</span></span></span></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_Vidguk_Keriv_Bakalavr-2020.docx\"> <strong> Feedback from the head of the DP </strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://scs.wp.its-my.site/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/scs.its-my.site_images_ZahystDocs_Recensiya_DP_Bakalavr-2020.doc\"> <strong> DP Review </strong> </a>\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"color: # b22222;\"> <strong> No later than 5 days before protection </strong></span> </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><strong> documents must be submitted to the EC Secretary </strong></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><strong> Kuchmiy Oksana Oleksandrivna (104 / 2-15k): </strong></p>\n\n<ol>\n 	<li>Booklet and signed diploma project (work).</li>\n</ol>\n<ul class=\"rteindent1\">\n 	<li><strong> <u> Title page </u> </strong> indicating the educational-professional program (according to the enrollment order, see above) and specialty <span style=\"color: # 800080;\"> <strong> <u> 123 \"Computer Engineering\" </u> </strong> </span>), topics, name of the student, supervisor, consultants, reviewer, etc., where <strong> should be all signatures </strong>;</li>\n 	<li><strong> <u> TASKS on the BF </u> </strong> with mandatory indication of the number and date of the order (<span style=\"color: # ff0000;\"> <span style=\"\"> N <u> 1181-С </u> </span> </span> from <span style=\"color: # ff0000;\"> <span style=\"\"> <u> 25.05.2020 </u> </span> </span> ) and calendar plan;</li>\n 	<li><strong><u>Annotations</u> </strong> (in Ukrainian and English languages ​​on separate sheets)</li>\n 	<li><strong> <u> ALBUM DESCRIPTION </u> </strong> (first sheet - with large corner stamp, where <strong> all captions should be </strong>);</li>\n 	<li><strong> <u> SPECIFICATION </u> </strong> (first sheet - with a large corner stamp, where <strong> all signatures should be </strong>);</li>\n 	<li><strong> <u> TECHNICAL PROJECT STATEMENT </u> </strong> (first sheet - with a large corner stamp, where <strong> all signatures should be </strong>);</li>\n 	<li><strong> <u> EXPLANATORY NOTE </u> </strong> (first sheet - with a large corner stamp, where all signatures should be - TABLE OF CONTENTS), which ends with a LIST OF USED LITERATURE (according to DSTU GOST 7.1: 2006 ) - NOT LESS THAN 50 SHEETS;</li>\n 	<li><strong><u>APPENDERS</u> </strong>:</li>\n</ul>\n; graphics - with a large corner stamp, where <strong> all captions should be </strong>,\n\n; listing of programs (s);\n\n<strong> presentation </strong>.\n<ol start=\"2\">\n 	<li>CD with materials of the diploma project (works).</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 35.45pt;\">The information recorded on the disk should be structured as follows:</p>\n\n<ul class=\"rteindent1\">\n 	<li>TEXT folder;</li>\n 	<li>GRAPH folder;</li>\n 	<li>PROGRAM folder;</li>\n 	<li>PREZENTATION folder</li>\n 	<li>WEBSITE folder (contains a file with annotations in Ukrainian and English, which will be placed on the website of the department).</li>\n</ul>\n<span style=\"color: # ff0000;\"> <strong> The name of each file must start with the name of the author of the project in Ukrainian !!! </strong> </span>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 35.45pt;\">The disk must have a <strong> supervisor\'s signature </strong>. This disk must be enclosed in an envelope that is glued to the inside of the cover at the end of the bound diploma project.</p>\n\n<ol>\n 	<li value=\"4\">Stitched copies of presentation slides (4 copies) - NOT REQUIRED in 2020</li>\n 	<li value=\"5\">Review required with SEAL.</li>\n 	<li value=\"6\">Manager feedback (+ scoreboard on a separate sheet).</li>\n 	<li>The first page of a plagiarism check on UNICHECK.</li>\n 	<li>Copies of published articles, abstracts of reports, acts (certificates) on implementation (if any).</li>\n</ol>\nMore information can be read here: <a href=\"http://www.fpm.kpi.ua/faculty/diploma.do\"> http://www.fpm.kpi.ua/faculty/diploma.do </a>\n\n<strong> After passing the normative control, the diploma project is signed by the head of the SPiSKS department Romankevich VO </strong> <strong> not later than three days before the defense </strong> <strong> in 102-15 k. &lt; / strong&gt; </strong>\n\n<strong> Persons whose diploma project is not signed by the head of the department are NOT ALLOWED to defend! </strong>\n\n<strong> Penalty points will be imposed for late submission of the above documents, as well as for their improper execution (see table) </strong>\n\n<strong> <u> The order of preparation of the diploma project for defense </u> </strong>\n<ol>\n 	<li>Bound BF and graphic material are signed by the author, supervisor, reviewer responsible for regulatory control.</li>\n 	<li><span style=\"color: # ff0000;\"> The CD with the materials of the SOE is signed by the head and pasted in an envelope on the cover of the SOE. At <span id=\"cloak66f1ead5e9bb7985969f80038197969b\"> <a href=\"mailto:ok_kuch@i.ua\"> ok_kuch@i.ua </a> </span> the contents of the WEBSITE folder are sent. <span style=\"color: # ff0000;\"> <strong> The name of each file must start with the name of the author of the project in Ukrainian !!! </strong> </span> </span></li>\n 	<li>BF together with the review, response and table of evaluation results from the head (link to the sample in electronic form see above) and graphic materials provided to the secretary of the examination commission (subject to receipt of files by e-mail to place materials BF on the website of the department). / li&gt;</li>\n 	<li>Approved by the head of the department of the State Enterprise together with all the necessary documentation is finally submitted to the secretary of the examination commission.</li>\n 	<li>DP materials will be posted on the department\'s website.</li>\n 	<li>DP protection is on schedule.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>', 'Documentation for Defense - Bachelors', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '207-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-06-04 21:45:49', '2021-06-04 21:45:49', '', 207, 'https://wp.scs.its-my.site/?p=975', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
